name: Nft dream
description:
Piece #3 of the collection:
I'm not your therapist but I'd like to cheer you up with my dorky art

The series focuses on the fragility of the inner world and brings up topics that we often find in our long journey on earth. 

Nft is my life-changer. Finally, I can call myself an artist.
For so many years I worked in the creative industry, always promoting a product, a brand. I had always compromised my art for something capitalistic. With Nft, I'm free to sell my art without any compromise.
